quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  36,31,"Miyeyna ogaan intee baan facyo halaagnay hortood, aan xaggooda u soo noqonayn?"
  36,32,"Kulligoodna iyagoo dhan Hortayadaa la keeni."
  36,33,"Waxaa Calaamo u ah arlada meydka ah aanu nooleyno, kana soo saarno hadhuudh ay wax ka cunaan."
  37,16,"Ma markaan dhimanno oo aan noqonno carro iyo lafo, miyaa nala soo bixin?"
  37,17,"Iyo aabbayaashayadii hore (iyagana ma la so bixin dhimasho kaddib)?."
  37,18,"Dheh: Haah, idinkoo waliba dulleysan."
